Camoflage::

She smiled up at the bot. "Well, uh, Windlord right? Well, the 
sickness came. Mom and Dad didn't want me to get sick. So they sent 
me away. Are we the only ones here? I thought I was the only one 
left."  She transformed into fox mode and started to hop, jump and 
run around Windlord. "But now that you are here, wanna play?" She 
tapped her paw against his leg,"TAG! Your IT!" and darted off down 
the path.
